Value.Help:
Configuration Value 1: 1‐255 Configuration Value 1 is to Specify the time that Smart Switch need blink, The unit is Second;
Configuration Value 2: 1‐255 Configuration Value 2 is to Specify the Cycle of on/off, the unit of it is 0.1 second. For example: if we set Configuration Value 1 to '15',Configuration Value 2 to '10',then Smart Switch will open 0.5 second, close 0.5 second, and repeat for 14 times.
Default value 0x0f0a
